"To change the format and appearance of selected cell(s), row(s) or column(s) "
"use the <guimenuitem>Cell Format...</guimenuitem> option from the "
"<guimenu>Format</guimenu> menu or from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
"mouse button popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Guhindura... i Imiterere na Imigaragarire Bya Byahiswemo Akazu ( S ) , "
"Urubariro ( S ) Cyangwa Inkingi ( S ) Koresha i <guimenuitem> ... </"
"guimenuitem> Ihitamo Kuva: i <guimenu> </guimenu> Ibikubiyemo Cyangwa Kuva: "
"i <mousebutton> Iburyo: </mousebutton> Imbeba Akabuto Hejuru Ibikubiyemo . "

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:43
