"<guisubmenu> </guisubmenu> <guimenuitem> </guimenuitem> </menuchoice> . "

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:555
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Merging Cells"
msgstr "Guhuza Utuzu"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:556
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is often convenient to have one cell that spreads across two or more "
"columns or down more than one row. This can be done by merging two or more "
"cells into one. Select the cells to be merged than choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu> Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Merge Cells</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"ni Kuri Rimwe Akazu Kwambukiranya Kabiri Cyangwa Birenzeho Inkingi: Cyangwa "
"Hasi Birenzeho Rimwe Urubariro . Byakozwe ku Kabiri Cyangwa Birenzeho "
"Utudirishya Rimwe . i Utudirishya Kuri Hitamo... <menuchoice> <guimenu> </"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem> </guimenuitem> </menuchoice> . "

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:560
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To reverse this process, select the merged cell then choose <guimenuitem> "
"Dissociate Cells</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Format</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Ihindurakerekezo iyi , Guhitamo i Akazu Hanyuma Hitamo... <guimenuitem> </"
"guimenuitem> Kuva: i <guimenu> </guimenu> Ibikubiyemo . "

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:565
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Hiding Rows and Columns"
msgstr "na "

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:566
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A finished spreadsheet can often be made to look more attractive by hiding "
"the cells containing intermediate calculations so that only the important "
"data input and result areas are shown."
msgstr ""
"A Byarangiye Urupapuro rusesuye Kuri Kureba Birenzeho ku i Utudirishya i "
"By'ingirakamaro Ibyatanzwe Iyinjiza na Igisubizo Ubuso . "

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:569
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &sheets; you can hide selected rows or columns by using the "
"<guimenuitem>Hide Rows</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Hide Columns</"
"guimenuitem> options from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Row</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenu>Format </"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Column</guisubmenu></menuchoice> or <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> mouse button menus. Hidden rows and columns are not displayed "
"on the screen or included in a print out."
msgstr ""
"&kspread; Gushisha Byahiswemo Urubariro: Cyangwa Inkingi: ku ikoresha i "
"<guimenuitem> </guimenuitem> na <guimenuitem> </guimenuitem> Amahitamo Kuva: "
"i <menuchoice> <guimenu> </guimenu> <guisubmenu> </guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> , <menuchoice> <guimenu> </guimenu> <guisubmenu> </guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> Cyangwa <mousebutton> Iburyo: </mousebutton> Imbeba Akabuto "
"Ibikubiyemo . Urubariro: na Inkingi: OYA ku i Mugaragaza Cyangwa in A "
"&Shyira ku rupapuro... Inyuma . "

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:576
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hiding cells in this way also makes them slightly less prone to accidental "
"change."
msgstr "Utudirishya in iyi Birutwa Kuri Guhindura... . "

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:578
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To un-hide a row or column select <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Row </"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Show Rows...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Column</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Show Columns...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> from the <guimenu>Format</guimenu> menu. In the "
"dialog box which appears, you can select any number of rows to show."
msgstr ""
"- Gushisha A Urubariro Cyangwa Inkingi Guhitamo <menuchoice> <guisubmenu> </"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem> ... </guimenuitem> </menuchoice> Cyangwa "
"<menuchoice> <guisubmenu> </guisubmenu> <guimenuitem> ... </guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> Kuva: i <guimenu> </guimenu> Ibikubiyemo . i Ikiganiro "
